      public Restaurant​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String address, java.lang.String city, java.lang.String state, java.lang.String telephone, int seatcapacity)
      Given the params, create a new restaurant object.

      restaurantid is autogenerated.

      Parameters:
      name - The name (String) of the restaurant.
      address - The address (String) of the restaurant.
      city - The city (String) of the restaurant.
      state - The state (String) of the restaurant.
      telephone - The telephone number (String) of the restaurant.
      seatcapacity - The seating capacity (Integer) of the restaurant. menus are added outside of this constructor.
